\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Jon 8:33,39\x*K…®miaha tiham…ôkeikei mho noien amasan me trahat…ôn pen m…ô k…®miaha hi…ôn…ôpw…ôh p…ôrhien noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôk…®miaha. R…ôr…ôha k…®miaha tih…ôni pen tukumiaha me i m…ô Epraham in kaha s…ôk…®miaha. Iakani pehe tukumiaha i m…ô Kumwes…ôn rukur…ôn nuvehiien k…ôru…ôterei me i, mo n…®pwn…ôti Epraham me ia nir…ôha.
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt Mat 7:19\x*In r…®n…ôrpwi pen raka paha s…ôv…ônhi ia nuai nei me na tr…ôrai. Nei me pam s…ôm…ôme h…ôpkuku…ô mh…ô nukwai nei amasan in tr…ôrai …ômwesi, mous…ô pen ir…ôha ia napw.‚Äù
