\p M…®re…°i Jon r…®ni pen t…® nir…ôha i m…ô, ‚ÄúK…®miaha tih…ôpw…ôh n…ôkeikeiien m n…ôrmama mheiku…ô ia nir…ôha m…ô tiho n…ômis…ôien m…®nraha tr…®ni m…®nu…ô h…ôpkuvei pehe mh…ô mane m k…®miaha. Rer…®miaha tram…ôkeikei ma…°ien t…® n…ôr…ôkuien s…ôk…®miaha.‚Äù
