\q1 Josef in t…®ni Heli.\f + \fr 3:23 \ft S…ôtoni m…ô Matiu in mwi r…®m…ôrai pen kw…ôn…ôkwus s…ôv…ôi Iesu ia n…ôkuku…ô s…ôv…ônhi (Mat 1:1-17), m…ôt…ô kw…ôn…ôkwus n…ôha Matiu r…®m…ôrai rop…ô ia kw…ôn…ôkwus i Luk r…®m…ôrai. Kw…ôn…ôkwus mi n…ôha kroupk…ômwhen mh…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Matiu rostat ia Epraham mauvehe mamesi pen kw…ôn…ôkwus s…ôv…ôi Ki…° Tev…®t m…®ne t…®ni n…ô…°h…®n n…ô Solomon, m…ôt…ô Luk rostat ia Iesu mamr…ôr…®…° mamesi pen kw…ôn…ôkwus s…ôv…ôi Ki…° Tev…®t m…®ne t…®ni n…ô…°h…®n n…ô Natan. Rosi Luk in rani kw…ôn…ôkwus s…ôv…ôi Meri, m…ôt…ô Matiu in rani kw…ôn…ôkwus s…ôv…ôi Josef. M…ô n…®p…ôrhienien Luk rani kw…ôn…ôkwus s…ôv…ôi Meri, suatuk riti mwi t…® n…®niien kw…ôti n…ô…°kiariien ia vas 23 in i m…ô: ‚ÄúN…ôrmama me rer…®nraha ramrhi m…ô in t…®ni Josef, m…ôt…ô rek…ôm. In t…®ni Meri. Tata s…ôv…ôi Meri in Heli.‚Äù\f*
