\v 21 \x - \xo 5:21 \xt Luk 7:49, Aes 43:25\x*N…ôp…®n nahat…ôn me s…ôv…ôi Loa m…®ne Farisi me h…ôre…°i n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha, h…ônam…ôres ir…ôha me i m…ô, ‚ÄúSin i i…ôrmama i rani …ôr…ôha Kumwes…ôn iam…®nhi? Kumwes…ôn …ôpa rukur…ôn nenouenouien noien …ôr…ôha me. Sin mwi rukur…ôn noien?‚Äù
