\v 24 \x - \xo 5:24 \xt Jon 5:8\x*M…ôt…ô iakokeikei m…ô k…®miaha tih…ôukur…ôn m…ô iou, I…ôm…ôti I…ôrmama, iakauvehi nasoriien ia t…®pr…ôn…ô i. Iakukur…ôn nenouenouien noien …ôr…ôha me.‚Äù N…ôn…ô Iesu r…®ni pen t…® i…ôrmama s…ô n…®sun mi krouemh…ô m…ô, ‚ÄúIakani pehe tukw ik i m…ô …ôrer, muvehi n…®m…ôhan s…ôim, mav…ôn mamev…ôn fwe imwam.‚Äù
\v 25 T…ôkwt…ôkwuni a i…ôrmama n…ôha r…ôrer ia n…ômr…®nraha, muvehi n…®m…ôhan s…ôv…ônhi, mamev…ôn fwe imw…ôni, mam…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni Kumwes…ôn.
\v 26 N…ôrmama me pam h…ôtoni, h…ôhek…®r. N…ônimenraha rier. H…ôuvehi ut…ô n…ô…°hi Kumwes…ôn, mamh…ôni m…ô, ‚ÄúKwa k…®taha i s…ôn…ôtoni narimnari me nepw…®n ipwet rus…ôp…ô.‚Äù
