\v 49 \x - \xo 23:49 \xt Sam 38:11, 88:8, Luk 8:2-3\x*N…ôrmama me pam s…ôm…ôme h…ôukur…ôn Iesu, m…®ne n…®pran me n…ôha s…ôm…ôme h…ônam…ôkurir…ô in fwe ia t…ôn…ô Kalili, kamh…ôrer isipw…®n, mamh…ôspau ia narimnari me n…ôha.
